        is currently teaching at the Hungarian Adventist Theological
        Seminary. Her research focuses on individuals' gain of self
        consciousness and its obstacles. She consideres preaching the
        greatest challenge of her life. She feels the greatest miracle
        she has experienced was the birth of faith in her. She lives
        with her husband in Budapest.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-6 columns">
      <h2>Zoltán Szallós-Farkas</h2>
      <span class="th"><%= image_tag '2015/zoltan.jpg' %></span>
      <p>
